Einstein Discovery

Create a Model from a Dataset
Create a model to uncover meaningful relationships among variables in a CRM Analytics dataset.
Einstein Discovery augments analysis by quickly sifting through huge amounts of data to uncover statistically significant correlations.

Create a Model from a Template
Quickly create a model using Einstein Discovery model templates. Each template provides a starter implementation for a common use case.
Model templates give you what you need to build the app, prepare and load your data, create an initial model, deploy a model, and save predictions into your CRM Analytics dataset.

Create a Model from a Lens
Quickly create a model from a CRM Analytics lens. After creating a lens to explore your data, you can easily get insights directly from the lens.
Filters that are applied to the lens get persisted saving time with model setup.

Cancel Model Creation
You can cancel model creation before Einstein finishes creating it.
Canceling a model interrupts Einstein data analysis and abandons any model elements created after clicking Create Model.
